{
  "$schema": "https://openapi.vercel.sh/vercel.json",
  "framework": "nextjs",
  "buildCommand": "npm run build",
  "crons": [
    {
      "path": "/api/cron/process",
      "schedule": "0 0 * * *"
    }
  ]
}
```

Save it, then run:
```
git add vercel.json
git commit -m "fix cron schedule for hobby plan"
git push origin main
```

Then:
```
npx vercel --prod